data.description: This spacious and inviting property is perfect for families looking for a comfortable place to call home. The house boasts 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms.As you enter the home, you will be greeted by the warm and inviting living room, the perfect space for relaxing with family and friends. The kitchen is fully equipped with modern appliances and ample counter space, making meal preparation a breeze. Just off the kitchen, you will find a cozy dining area that's perfect for family meals.The bedrooms are spacious and offer plenty of natural light, making them great spaces for rest and relaxation. The backyard is also a great space for children to play and enjoy the outdoors. (SEE MORE) This home is located in a quiet and family-friendly neighborhood, providing a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of the city. This home comes with 13 solar panels, purchased last December. Initial cost was $46,810 for the system producing 11,574 kwh annually. The system has a remaining balance of $25,979, solar tax credit granted 13,000 going towards the balance owed, coming soon. This Leaving a $117 monthly payment.
